  "2026-07-05T10:35:20.368Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: bootstrap initially failed under pnpm 11 because package.json#pnpm was ignored and build scripts were left as pnpm-workspace allowBuilds placeholders. Migrated reviewed build-script decisions and overrides into pnpm-workspace.yaml; reran pnpm config list and pnpm build successfully."
