  "2026-07-05T11:01:22.707Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: addressed local Greptile pre-push finding by adding create-command regression coverage for self-parent rejection plus internal explicit-id normalization, invalid-id, and duplicate-id protection. Focused suite passed afterward: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/commands/create-command.spec.ts tests/unit/commands/update-command.spec.ts tests/unit/core/item/item-record.spec.ts tests/unit/core/item/core-item-lock-coverage.spec.ts (4 files, 271 tests)."
