  "2026-07-05T11:08:45.455Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: final release/package checks passed after the post-Greptile patch. pnpm contracts:check passed, pnpm security:scan found no credential-like secrets, pnpm audit --audit-level moderate found no known vulnerabilities, and pnpm changelog:pm:check with pm-changelog 2026.6.30 left CHANGELOG.md unchanged. Final installed-package smoke passed from npm pack tarball in /tmp/tmp.f8x0Q2YQTl with isolated PM_PATH/PM_GLOBAL_PATH: init, create, self-parent update rejection, comments, get, health, validate, and SDK primitive export checks."
  "2026-07-05T11:14:28.463Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: fresh Greptile pre-push review passed after the create-command regression was added. Review 2099fb2a-f1f5-4862-8a26-e522d90232e4 reported confidence 5/5, safe to merge, and no review comments."
  "2026-07-05T11:15:19.014Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: opened PR #434 Fix self-parent guards and pnpm 11 bootstrap gates: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/pull/434"
  "2026-07-05T11:38:16.075Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: addressed post-PR bot feedback locally by registering pm create --id through the SDK commander contract, rejecting explicit create id placeholder tokens none/null/undefined, rejecting non-string parent values in the shared parent-reference primitive, and aligning packageManager plus GitLab/Jenkins examples to pnpm@11.10.0. Focused regression passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/commands/create-command.spec.ts tests/unit/commands/update-command.spec.ts tests/unit/core/item/item-record.spec.ts tests/unit/core/item/core-item-lock-coverage.spec.ts (4 files, 272 tests). Full coverage passed: 263 files / 5419 tests with 100% statements, branches, functions, and lines. Gates passed: pnpm build, pnpm typecheck, pnpm contracts:check, pnpm lint, pnpm security:scan, pnpm audit --audit-level moderate, pnpm changelog:pm:check. Manual installed-package smoke passed from npm pack in /tmp/tmp.t399Ppjrpn: init, create --id, get, self-parent create rejection before writes, comments, health, validate, and SDK getWorkspaceContracts/composeExtension/defineExtensionManifest exports."
  "2026-07-05T11:54:14.271Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: GitHub checks on head 1f75050e exposed pnpm/action-setup version mismatch because workflows still pinned 10.33.4 while package.json declared packageManager pnpm@11.10.0. Updated ci/docs/nightly/release/auto-release workflows plus the GitHub Actions extension-gate example to pnpm 11.10.0. Regenerated contracts snapshot after build surfaced the new create --id contract. Verification passed: pinned actionlint 1.7.12 over all workflows; pnpm build; pnpm typecheck; pnpm quality:docs-skills; pnpm quality:docs-links; pnpm contracts:check; focused contract/help runtime suite (4 files, 124 tests)."
  "2026-07-05T11:59:23.528Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: addressed latest bot feedback. Gemini path traversal finding is fixed by validating explicit create IDs after normalization with a filename-safe alphanumeric/dash pattern; shorthand #SAFE-SHORTHAND-ID still normalizes safely while ../traversal, slash, backslash, colon, and dot-prefixed IDs are rejected before lookup/write. Greptile workflow-pin finding is fixed by aligning all real pnpm/action-setup workflow pins to 11.10.0. Verification passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/commands/create-command.spec.ts tests/unit/core/item/item-record.spec.ts tests/unit/scripts/contracts-snapshot.spec.ts tests/unit/commands/contracts-command.spec.ts (4 files, 176 tests); pnpm typecheck; pnpm contracts:check."
  "2026-07-05T12:24:55.020Z",unknown,"Evidence: final post-bot-feedback gates passed after aligning SDK getContracts create flag surface. pnpm build passed; pnpm contracts:update regenerated tests/fixtures/contracts/full.json and pnpm contracts:check passed; focused suite passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/commands/contracts-command.spec.ts tests/unit/scripts/contracts-snapshot.spec.ts tests/integration/ci-workflow-contract.spec.ts tests/unit/commands/create-command.spec.ts (4 files, 172 tests). Installed-package smoke passed from npm pack tarball in /tmp/tmp.IIgzHA0MSD: init, create --id, get, invalid traversal id rejection, create self-parent rejection, comments, health, validate, getWorkspaceContracts schema primitives, getContracts create --id flag, and composeExtension/defineExtensionManifest SDK exports. Final coverage passed across 263 files / 5419 tests with 100% statements, branches, functions, and lines; pnpm lint passed with ESLint, jscpd 0 clones, and static quality; pnpm security:scan found no credential-like secrets; pnpm audit --audit-level moderate found no known vulnerabilities."
  "2026-07-05T12:45:11.413Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: addressed Greptile pre-push summary gap by adding a dedicated built-CLI integration regression for create --id self-parent rejection before writes. Verification passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/create-self-parent.integration.spec.ts (1 file, 1 test); pnpm build && pnpm contracts:check; pnpm lint with ESLint, jscpd 0 clones, and static quality; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed across 264 files / 5420 tests with 100% statements, branches, functions, and lines. Greptile also noted the exact undici override; duplicate-safe all-status search found canonical dependency-governance lineage pm-q71q, and current pnpm audit was already clean, so no duplicate pm item was created."
  "2026-07-05T13:03:52.442Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: addressed final Greptile quality observations by adding tests/unit/core/item/core-item-lock-coverage.spec.ts to the required per-PR Windows regression job and expanding the built-CLI self-parent integration regression to cover update --parent <same-id> while preserving the existing parent. Verification passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/create-self-parent.integration.spec.ts tests/integration/ci-workflow-contract.spec.ts tests/unit/core/item/core-item-lock-coverage.spec.ts (3 files, 60 tests); pnpm contracts:check; pnpm lint; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed across 264 files / 5421 tests with 100% statements, branches, functions, and lines."
  "2026-07-05T13:05:38.530Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: telemetry verification after final local gates showed telemetry enabled for https://pm-cli.unbrained.dev/v1/events with last_successful_flush_at 2026-07-05T13:04:22.208Z. An explicit pm telemetry flush attempted at 2026-07-05T13:04:55.321Z but did not drain the local queue because the endpoint request timed out; pm health remains ok with the non-blocking telemetry_queue_pending warning."
  "2026-07-05T13:07:11.697Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: final local Greptile invocation 76921ee0-f227-473c-a0d0-52fb52a98f00 reused a cached result and repeated stale findings after they were fixed. Current files include tests/unit/core/item/core-item-lock-coverage.spec.ts in .github/workflows/ci.yml Windows regression command and include the built-CLI update self-parent integration case in tests/integration/create-self-parent.integration.spec.ts. A fresh remote bot review will be requested after push."
  "2026-07-05T13:30:07.845Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: addressed latest CodeRabbit findings locally. Dependency override ranges are now bounded to the next major in pnpm-workspace.yaml and pnpm-lock.yaml; the explicit create-id duplicate check now runs inside writeCreatedItem after acquireLock and before writeFileAtomic; the broad create explicit-id unit test is split into normalized, invalid, and locked duplicate-conflict cases; and the GitHub Actions extension-gate example now installs pnpm before setup-node enables pnpm cache. Verification passed after these changes: pnpm install --lockfile-only; pnpm build; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/commands/create-command.spec.ts tests/integration/ci-workflow-contract.spec.ts tests/integration/create-self-parent.integration.spec.ts (3 files, 126 tests); pnpm contracts:check; pnpm security:scan; pnpm audit --audit-level moderate; pnpm lint with ESLint, jscpd 0 clones, and static quality; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed across 264 files / 5423 tests with 100% statements, branches, functions, and lines."
  "2026-07-05T14:02:29.955Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: addressed Greptile pre-push UX finding by preserving original typed parent/item values in self-parent errors when normalization collapses them to the same id. Added direct coverage for both normalized-detail and already-normalized message branches. Stabilized the subprocess-heavy completion runtime-config regression with a scoped 90s timeout after full-suite coverage load exposed a 30s timeout despite the file passing in isolation. Verification passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/core/item/item-record.spec.ts tests/unit/commands/completion-command.spec.ts; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed across 264 files / 5423 tests with 100% statements, branches, functions, and lines."
  "2026-07-05T14:03:27.759Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: final static quality after Greptile UX/test-stability edits passed: pnpm lint completed with ESLint clean, jscpd 0 clones, and static quality gate passed."
  "2026-07-05T14:08:44.333Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: addressed Greptile dependency-policy finding by changing esbuild, undici, and vite workspace overrides from exact pins to bounded same-major ranges in pnpm-workspace.yaml and pnpm-lock.yaml. Verification passed: pnpm install --lockfile-only; pnpm audit --audit-level moderate; pnpm security:scan; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/commands/create-command.spec.ts tests/unit/core/item/item-record.spec.ts (2 files, 128 tests); pnpm contracts:check; pnpm changelog:pm:check with pm-changelog 2026.6.30 unchanged; pnpm lint with ESLint, jscpd 0 clones, and static quality."
  "2026-07-05T14:30:06.026Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: addressed final CodeRabbit placeholder-token drift finding by extracting shared isPlaceholderReferenceToken in src/core/item/parent-reference-policy.ts and reusing it in pm create --id validation. Verification passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/core/item/item-record.spec.ts tests/unit/commands/create-command.spec.ts (2 files, 128 tests); pnpm lint with ESLint, jscpd 0 clones, and static quality; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed across 264 files / 5423 tests with 100% statements, branches, functions, and lines."
