close_reason: "Closed after final CodeRabbit follow-up: shared placeholder-token detection is extracted and reused by create explicit-id validation; focused tests, lint, and full coverage 100/100/100/100 across 264 files / 5423 tests passed."
body: "Duplicate check before create: searched all statuses for GH-433 parent self-cycle/write-time prevention, pnpm 11 allowBuilds/overrides/bootstrap ignored-builds, and Windows acquireStaleCleanupGate lock coverage. Existing matches were broader closed history or parent epics; no canonical live item covered this combined implementation bundle. Related live items: pm-lt6n for GH-427 Windows nightly, pm-7zs0 for release-health verification, pm-5566 for the docstring gate that currently blocks Auto Release, and pm-98cz for lifecycle primitive correctness."
